title: The Mike Rosen Radio Show NOV-26-2013 TUES
description:
The Mike Rosen Radio Show NOV-26-2013 TUES





Tuesday, November 26, 2013
Obamacare House Testimony

 
 

 - 9AM hour

CGI House testimony concerning privacy warning on the Obamacare website.

 

 - 10AM hour

1. Mike deconstructs a letter to the editor complaining about retail stores
          opening on Thanksgiving. 
2. Why Black Friday is an illusion.



 - 11AM hour

Guest: Erik Prince, Founder of Blackwater, Inc.
          "Civilian Warriors: The Inside Story of Blackwater
                         and the Unsung Heroes of the War on Terror."
